{
  "texts": [
    "A specific prompt pattern is implemented to each specified pain point.",
    "In conversations with GenAI different types of prompts: explicit, implicit, and creative can be used.",
    "Explicit prompts are direct and clear instructions given to the AI model about the specific format or information needed in the output.",
    "On the other hand, implicit prompts are less direct and give the AI model more flexibility to interpret the intended result.",
    "Creative prompts aim to inspire AI models to produce original, imaginative, or unconventional outputs [28]."
  ]
}